ure has the capacity to enlarge preexisting holes and lower\ntheir creation energies, helping to bridge the gap between the observed star\nformation rate and that required to create the holes. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2001 17:14:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
